import Home from './Home'
import Other from './Other'
import PageNotFound from './PageNotFound'
import { FaHome } from 'react-icons/fa'
import { IoIosSettings } from 'react-icons/io'

const pagesList = [
    {
        name: "Accueil",
        icon: <FaHome style={{verticalAlign: 'top', paddingTop: '10%'}}/>,
        path: "/home",
        app: <Home />,
        title: "Accueil de l'application"
    },
    {
        name: "Paramètres",
        icon: <IoIosSettings style={{verticalAlign: 'top', paddingTop: '10%'}}/>,
        path: "/other",
        app: <Other />,
        title: "Paramètres de l'application"
    },
    {
        name: "PageNotFound",
        path: "/pageNotFound",
        app: <PageNotFound />,
        hidden: true,
        title: "Ouch..."
    }
]

export default pagesList;
